  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators propose to conduct a study to measure the reproducibility of CMR parameters
      that have been used to predict outcome following PPCI: infarct size, left ventricular
      volumes, myocardial salvage, microvascular obstruction (MVO) and myocardial oedema.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
